sv:property.sv:value: A summary text for the medewerker that will be displayed in overview page and search results. The first image coming from the flexible block will be considered as the medewerker profile picture. The selected lectoraten will determine the lectoraten where the medewerker will be displayed. for the rest is just a normal page that can be build via flexible block elements, except for the fact that it does not have a header image.
